data.description: Step into this charming 6-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence nestled in the sought-after Royal Oaks neighborhood. Boasting ample room for all and friends, this home is situated on an expansive double lot, featuring a delightful in-ground pool that adds a touch of summer entertainment. A little tender loving care will transform this property into the crown jewel of the community.  Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by an inviting living room, setting the tone for a warm and comfortable ambiance. The generously sized kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, abundant counter space, and ample storage, catering to the needs of any home chef. The primary bedroom suite includes a private ensuite bathroom, while the additional bedrooms offer generous proportions and showcase new flooring throughout.  Adding to the appeal, the home boasts a finished lower level, providing versatile space for a home theater, game room, or an extra living area in the sixth bedroom. The backyard is a haven with its inground pool and expansive patio, offering a perfect retreat for relaxation or entertaining.  Nestled in the highly desirable Royal Oaks neighborhood, this home is conveniently located near Indiana Beach, parks, shopping, and dining options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this residence your own.
